<div class="row">
  <div class="jumbotron">
    <div class="col-md-5 col-xs-6">
      <div class="pull-right">
        <%= image_tag("clock.svg", :alt => "Time Task It Logo", :class => "img-responsive") %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-7 col-xs-6">
      <div class="pull-left">
        <h1>Time Task It</h1>
        <p>In a sea of things to do, </br>prioritize your life!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container sign-up-band">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-5 col-md-offset-1">
      <%= link_to "Sign Up", new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn btn-default btn-lg pull-left breather-side' %>
      <h4 class="white-text breather">Sign up for Free today!</h4>
    </div>  
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row breather-xl"> 
  <div class="col-md-8 col-xs-8">
    <div class="background-box">
      <div class="inside-background-box text-center">
        <h4>Keep Your Lists Organized</h4>
        <hr/>
        <p class="hidden-xs">Most likely, you've got alot going on in your life.  Keep track of all those different aspects of life you're trying to juggle organized with customized lists.  Make as many as you need, to keep the tasks they contain seperate so you can focus on what you need when you have the time to do it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4 col-xs-4 center">
    <div class="breather">
      <%= image_tag("Octopus.svg", :alt => "Expired Tasks Self Destruct", :class => "img-responsive") %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row breather-xl"> 
  <div class="col-md-4 col-xs-4 center">
    <%= image_tag("Shark.svg", :alt => "Expired Tasks Self Destruct", :class => "img-responsive") %>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-8 col-xs-8">
    <div class="background-box">
      <div class="inside-background-box text-center">
        <h4>Keep Up on Upcomming Deadlines</h4>
        <hr/>
        <p class="hidden-xs">Forgot about something?  We keep track of all of your upcoming deadlines and put them in one place on your start screen.  All upcomming tasks are displayed so that if there is something coming up on a list you've forgotten about, it will come out of hiding.  We help you manage all the tasks that ussually fall into obscurity.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
</div>

<div class="row breather-xl"> 
  <div class="col-md-8 col-xs-8">
    <div class="background-box">
      <div class="inside-background-box text-center">
        <h4>Get Rid of Unwanted Clutter</h4>
        <hr/>
        <p class="hidden-xs">To Do lists are notorius for collecting lots of clutter.  With TimeTaskIt, we take care of that for you!  When a task passes it's deadline, the task automatically self destructs.  No more cluttered to do lists with things you just haven't gotten around to doing.  Because, let's be honest, if you haven't gotten done by then you weren't going to get around to doing it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4 col-xs-4 center">
    <%= image_tag("deep-sea-mine.svg", :alt => "Expired Tasks Self Destruct", :class => "img-responsive") %>
  </div>
</div>

